nodes.text: This male served as a death trooper of the Galactic Empire's military. Stationed onboard Freighter 2716, the trooper was assigned to guard a kyber crystal which was to be delivered to Director Orson Callan Krennic under the command of DT-F16. He was shot by Sabine Wren when he attempted to fall back with his commander.
The character is voiced by Stephen Stanton, who also voiced Wilhuff Tarkin and AP-5 in Star Wars Rebels.
